Ques: You are given a string s. You need to reverse the string.

Example:

Input:
s = Geeks
Output: skeeG


Ans: class Reverse
{
    // Complete the function
    // str: input string
    public static String reverseWord(String str)
    {
        StringBuffer rev = new StringBuffer("");
        int len = str.length();
        
        for (int i = len - 1; i >= 0; i--) {
            char ch = str.charAt(i);
            rev.append(ch);
        }
    
    return rev.toString();
        
    }
}
